Well after further discussing it with Kara, due to the time that we do play, we don't think that it will be worth it now to move. After further analyzing this server, though it is a good idea and I would love to move, I think the server really is made for the people who LIVE EQ. The people who are on more then 5 hours a day. <br>
<br>
We thought of this because it does say that the Legends server they will be the first on quest and some items will be named after it's first founder. Well, we don't play a whole lot to do quests and stuff. Though I would love to be there with all the good GM events I am sure they are going to host, but you kinda have to have time to do it. <br>
<br>
Kara brought many good points to my attention. Being that we do not play a whole lot and if we were to pay more, the ratio of Payment VS. fun time gets smaller, thus is a waste of money. But if we did play more I know we would go. I like the idea. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
